// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1706 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 7de8ef2f-243b-5aa8-8e55-342b54209c2b

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*")
